[32m+[m[32m# Consistify ‚Äî Fitness Planner üåü[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m[![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-prototype-yellow)]()[m
[32m+[m[32m[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue)]()[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mConsistify is a responsive, accessible prototype for a personalized fitness planner that helps users:[m
[32m+[m[32m- Calculate maintenance calories (Mifflin‚ÄìSt Jeor) and suggested macros (protein / fat / carbs).[m
[32m+[m[32m- Generate and filter workout routines (home, gym, cardio, yoga) according to preferences and intensity.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Suggest budget-aware diet plans aiming to meet calorie & macro goals, prepared for integration with nutrition APIs to include micros, fiber and cost.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Offer sleep & recovery guidance tailored by age and activity level.[m
[32m+[m
